Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:04.54,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen years have passed since the start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the war between humans and demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:10.79,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,The humans entered the \NDemon Realm through the gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,taking one of the demons' strategic positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.41,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,But while human forces were deployed there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a demon forces occupied \None of the human territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:22.27,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,The small, frozen nations of the south
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fought many skirmishes with the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:28.44,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,And the ensuing chaos and destruction \Ncaused the people great suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:34.69,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst the nightmarish confusion, a hero arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with three companions, \Nhe went to defeat the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:41.40,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Their rapid advance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,brought the people of the \NCentral Nations great hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:50.21,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,But either because he was impatient at their \Nslow advance through the Demon Realm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:53.73,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps for some other reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:57.45,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,He left his party behind, heading alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toward the Demon King's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:04.01,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Like an arrow fired from a bow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:08.27,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,straighter than the line of a ruler...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:52.12,Title1a,,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:52.12,Title1b,,0000,0000,0000,,— You will be mine, Hero. \N— I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This castle is so large, \Nand yet no one is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:09.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Just up ahead is my foe, the Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Once I slay him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:17.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The long war with the demons
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:46.84,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.82,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:02.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.15,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm the Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Demon King a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.95,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's a traditional title.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.32,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.01,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The 43rd Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,My title is "The Ruby Eyes."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You really are the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.52,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have the crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Stop shoving your breasts in my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.63,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more, Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you're a woman or bouncy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.53,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero defeats the Demon King, \Nsaving everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's because
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,this is justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slice you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.09,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.04,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.05,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,"Hello again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so relaxed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.23,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:10.96,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've been awaiting your arrival
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.67,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,for such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.85,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking forward to speaking
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with you for such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, what am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.27,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Let the curtains rise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,...on the first, and perhaps last,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,play of the Hero and the Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, King of Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.86,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You will be mine, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:49.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.78,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:00.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many nations have \Nbeen destroyed because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.07,Default,Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Damned demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:06.34,Default,Mage,0000,0000,0000,,There's just no end to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:09.01,Default,Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This merely drains our stamina, without benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.29,Default,Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:18.79,Default,Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping is what makes me ultra happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:24.40,Default,Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Hero #1 left me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.96,Default,Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Like the Forest Country...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:31.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It was a beautiful country, filled with green.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And because of you demons, the sky blackened,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the people starved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:42.37,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If you start chopping down every \Ntree you find to make charcoal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,the pollution will ruin you eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Pollution?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.44,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't know what that is yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:52.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to fool me with your nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:57.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It was demons who possessed \Nthe Tin Country's minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:02.60,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Do evil, get caught, then claim \Ndemons were brainwashing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.17,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,A common way that human \Npoliticians evade responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:08.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What of your war with the Southern Nations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:13.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen the hundreds slain by \Ndemon armies, with my own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:17.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Demon King, I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.01,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Humans have killed demons, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Because demons are evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.52,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Who decided that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.96,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Then perhaps you ought to have been God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.08,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.54,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.22,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:45.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,An economic analysis of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know about economics?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.07,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:56.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's a summary of all the war's advantages,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as seen from one standpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:01.06,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,A war has no advantages!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.29,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,A toast to the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.95,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,Having the demons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a common enemy has united humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:13.91,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,Plague and famine are less common \Nthan at any time in five hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.61,Default,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,A toast to the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which brings great wealth \Nto the Central Nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.36,Default,Accountant,0000,0000,0000,,T-To the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.72,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,To the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:27.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:31.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is this something humans are okay with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:34.08,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The demons aren't so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:38.14,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, minor nobles and lords named \Nthemselves king, one after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.43,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,fighting long, bloody wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.63,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But now, they are all united in my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:48.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense, war has changed \Nboth demons and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That may be so, ultimately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:56.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't justify perpetuating the war,\Nor starting it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're a war criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:04.49,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I do understand that it \Nwasn't for your own benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accompany you, so give yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.45,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we cannot end this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.87,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:17.98,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:24.01,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Must we continue to fight the demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:28.18,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really the right course of action?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:32.95,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,Our kingdom has no fertile farmland.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:37.02,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,The huge war funds the Central Nations send us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only come because of the war effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.26,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,Remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:46.20,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,until this war began, we were \Non the verge of annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.70,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Central Nations
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,send the war-weary Southern Nations \Ncharitable funds to support their fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:56.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And the Southern Nations use the \Nmoney for food and other necessities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:02.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Central Nations are donating, \Nwhile getting nothing in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's all out of the goodness of their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:05.35,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:16.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.01,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to know what they gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:21.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.44,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Security?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.91,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Has the war stretched across \Nthe whole Human World?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:30.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Central Nations are like another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.21,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.12,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:02.84,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,A lamp that shows what's inside \Nthe mind of the one holding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.53,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we're looking at your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.53,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Balls held almost every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,bright lights, and plenty of delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:21.53,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And I've seen drunken nobles in vineyards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,As though
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there were no war at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.33,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.94,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,They can do this because of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.69,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say the war ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.15,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:37.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The whole world would be at peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:43.10,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Without all this consumption,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,exporters of the Central Nations would be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.34,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,There would be many unemployed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,many without enough food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:52.88,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hundreds of thousands would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:53.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.76,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And there is another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.01,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I explained how,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:06.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,due to the war, food is going \Nto nations lacking it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:07.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:11.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,your world's agricultural output hasn't \Nincreased by any significant measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,People still starve to death, here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.78,Default,Farmer Women,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.81,Default,Farmer Women,0000,0000,0000,,My sisters are inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.32,Default,Farmer,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're burning it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.72,Default,Farmer,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let the demonic sickness spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.72,Default,Farmer,0000,0000,0000,,Sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:32.66,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If the war ends, more kids will be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hundreds of thousands of people everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will know nothing but how to use their swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Survival requires food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But humans now can't produce enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.17,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That means hundreds of thousands...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:49.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even millions will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.45,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to tell them the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:56.86,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,That your breasts are smaller \Nthan everyone believes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.91,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.79,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:05.92,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,If we tell them he vanished alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will everyone assume he got scared and ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:13.00,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.54,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell them what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.36,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.35,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.99,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:33.22,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, the human kings also know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.67,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That if the war ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether they win or lose, \Nhumanity will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.23,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they sent you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:42.87,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,instead of their armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.80,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If the demons win,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll establish colonies, \Ntake slaves from the human world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then fight each other over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That will never be allowed to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.65,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If the humans win, they'll do \Nthe same to demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Humans would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.08,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Many worlds have fallen in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:19.75,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere I've always dreamed of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere I long to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The place you long to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.31,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.78,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever thought to yourself, \N"What lies beyond that hill?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:41.89,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever asked yourself, \N"Where is this boat going?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:45.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Often, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.74,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.99,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Hero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It excites you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You seem happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.04,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.31,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The world beyond this war, \Nthe one I've never seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:04.05,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I shall say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:07.32,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You will be mine, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:11.29,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,To find that which I long to see, \Nyet still have not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.56,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:14.79,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,My light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.30,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,My blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:21.86,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:26.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.37,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,There's no room for negotiation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.65,Default - italics,M,0000,0000,0000,,Stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.70,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.45,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me \Nwith those puppy dog eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:46.79,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient records claim
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.96,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I should offer you half of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.62,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You seem unimpressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No hero would accept that deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:58.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have to be some kind of idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.14,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:02.37,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly what happens \Nin the records I've read.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.18,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,For one thing, giving you fifty percent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,still divides the world between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:13.06,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We'd merely be exchanging the struggle between
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the human and demon worlds for one between \Nthe realms of the Hero and Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.83,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,So we won't take that route.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then negotiations have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:30.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I really feel like fighting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.54,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I can give you all, not half, of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:35.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:40.14,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:41.61,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.32,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You have a very foolish expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:51.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.17,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you sane?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.12,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:59.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I share with you how \Nfast my heart is beating?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:02.59,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.62,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We seem to have more room \Nto negotiate than earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.68,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I won't touch you without your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.51,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a late bloomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:16.01,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But owning me confers several advantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:17.78,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:20.15,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You could go beyond this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.37,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it won't be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.41,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I were to surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the human kings would hide it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the demons would soon crown a new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.90,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That is how necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.90,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,this war is for both parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.39,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But that's also why
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it's possible to end the war another way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.77,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,it would mean a new hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only for myself, but for the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:50.36,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:54.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,who you really are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the army's job to end a war,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:02.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,it's the king's job to find a place for it to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:04.67,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you wanted me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.75,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.34,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I truly do want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.91,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want someone to go to \Nthe other side with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're too close...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.18,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:21.56,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:25.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lacking in the physical,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,exterior attributes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the majority of males
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,look for in a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:38.66,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how flabby my upper arm is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:39.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.80,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all flabby...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:48.11,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,My chastity is the single thing \Nin which I can take pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.59,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I honor contracts above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:54.01,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,So a contract of this nature \Nwould bind me by my soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:57.05,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,with a strength, stronger than steel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:59.28,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,that will never fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.71,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I would stay by your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:06.78,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,In sickness and in health.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.29,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:14.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be killing a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:15.80,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:17.61,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot promise
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you will not stain your \Nhands before the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:24.33,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Both you and I would have to \Ndo many horrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:39.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand is freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.07,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's too cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.79,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to you, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to you, Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.81,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The contract is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:57.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:00.69,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's our first move?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.79,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I suppose we start with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be a long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.73,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:24.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.59,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:33.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:37.48,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I will never leave your side, Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:38.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You'll uphold your side of the bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:55.97,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:58.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.43,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Can I hug you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.08,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:19.99,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:21.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.79,Default - italics,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hug... Hug... Hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:25.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,D-Demon King...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.38,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You have to practice these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:31.77,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:38.24,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero... Hero! Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.66,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.24,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.42,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:51.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Those come off?
